{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "邱凤城在住宅设宴招待马如龙，小婉亲自买酒做菜伴伴。马如龙看着两人亲密串透，感到自己是多余的，却已信任邱凤城。然而邱凤城突然捍死小婉，并亲口披露了整个阴谋：他利用小婉作为掉聋用人的工具，在聚丰楼下毒杀小杜等人，再派杀手灭口，并利用金振林、彭天霸、冯超凡和绝大师作为证人，将罪名嫁给马如龙。邱凤城揭示自己就是“天杀”首脑，目的是制造江湖混乱。话未说完，他突然中毒倒地，病状与杜青莲一样。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "马如龙虽然不在乎，小婉却还是带着歉意解释：\"凤城很少在这里喝酒，也很少有朋友到这里来，这坛酒还是我刚才临时去买的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"凤城喜欢清静，不愿用下人，所以这里什么事都只好由我自己做了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "因为他已经完全信任邱凤城。他正想站起来的时候，邱凤城又在向他敬酒了，又拉着小婉的手，带着笑道：\"你一定也得敬他三杯，三大杯。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "小婉吃吃的笑，拼命摇头！\"我只能敬他一杯。\"",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "\"一定要敬三大杯。\"",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "\"三大杯喝下去一定会把我喝死。\"",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "\"你不喝我就捏死你。\"",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "小婉笑得更媚，眼波中已有了春情：\"我情愿被你捏死。\"",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "\"真的？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_wan",
      "speaker_name": "小婉",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "\"当然是真的。\"",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_xiao_wan",
      "text": "\"好，\"邱凤城带着笑，用一只手捏住小婉的咽喉，轻轻的说：\"那么我就真的捏死你。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"说谎是种坏习惯，我这人从来不说谎的。\"他带着笑道：\"我说真的要捏死她，我就真的捏死了她，所以我说的话你以后一定要相信。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "邱凤城笑得更愉快：\"你为什么不问我？为什么要捏死她？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "用不着别人问，他自己居然先说了出来。\"其实我早就准备捏死她的，从我看到她那天开始，因为她不但长得很好看，而且是个很痴心的女人，像她这样的女人，正好能配合我的计划。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "邱凤城居然又解释：\"我要让大家都知道，我已经有了这么样一个肯死心塌地跟着我的女人，已经跟我有了山盟海誓，誓死不分，大家才会相信我绝不想做碧玉夫人的女婿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"他叹了口气：\"其实我想得要命。\"",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "但是他竞争的对手太强，他自己也没有把握能入选。\"所以我定要先除去你们三个人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"要除去这三个人实在很不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"幸好我知道你们都是酒鬼，又碰巧知道小杜在聚丰楼订了一席酒菜。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"惟一让我想不到的是，你居然不喝酒。\"他接着又道：\"幸好我这人做事一向谨慎，早已留下了后招。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"冯超凡和绝大师却是完全不知情的，我故意要彭天霸请他们到聚丰楼去喝酒，再带他们到寒梅谷去，只不过为了要他们证明这件事，证明我绝对是清白无辜的，证明你才是凶手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "\"他微笑：\"可是你也不能怪我，只怪你自己运气不好，居然没有喝酒，居然没有死，如果你也死了，就不会有这些烦恼了。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "所以小婉非死不可。邱凤城看着马如龙。\"至于你，你死不死都已经没什么太大的关系了，因为大家都已认定了你是凶手，你不死对我反而有好处。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_rulong",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "\"有什么好处？\"马如龙终于能开口：\"我不死对你有什么好处？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "邱凤城",
      "listener": "char_ma_rulong",
      "text": "邱凤城叹息着，悠然道：\"难道你现在还没有想到我就是'天杀'的首脑？\n\n\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_rulong",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_qiu_feng_cheng",
      "text": "他忍不住要问：\"你为什么要把你自己的秘密告诉我？\n\n\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    }
  ],
